<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200811/42d71c0b5ab6471d9825dd64c191ba36.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">侠之大者 为国为民</span></img></p>
